high_descs: Turn around heading towards counter.  Turn right after refrigerator. Turn left to face stove.
Pick up pot from right lower burner on stove top.
Turn left and head towards table.  Turn right to face sink and counter.
Place pot on counter top, behind the apple and potato.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Place the apple in the pot on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot from the stove and place an apple in the pot.

high_descs: Move to the stove to the left of the fridge
Pick up a pot from the stove
Move to the left of the sink
Put the pot on the counter
Pick up an apple from the counter
Put the apple inside the pot

high_descs: Turn around and go to the back of the kitchen and find the stove.
Pick up the pot from the back burner.
Carry the pot and turn left to go down to the far counter on the right.
Place the pot on the counter, in the back behind the apple.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Place the apple in the pot on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot to a different location and place an apple inside.
